For reference, a hot venti drink is 2.5 cups & a cold venti drink is 3 cups. So why was she complaining about expensive coffee at coffee shops, while still selling coffee at the same price... & that’s not even factoring in the cream/sugar/whatever else you’re adding in... so, honestly, am I missing something? It’s a really great idea, I just don’t see how complaining about expensive coffee while selling expensive coffee isn’t hypocritical.
